FT  26 MAR 93 / UK Company News: North Sea Assets down
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Reduced demand for drilling support services meant pre-tax profits of North
Sea Assets slipped from Pounds 2.08m to Pounds 1.95m in 1992.
Turnover dropped to Pounds 21.6m (Pounds 29.1m). Earnings per share were
